%% Solution — handoff → durable inbox → claim → card/conv round-trip
sequenceDiagram
  participant Alice as Alice host
  participant Relay as Relay
  participant Bob as Bob host
  participant Agent as Bob agent MCP

  Alice->>Relay: handoff @bob "fix auth"
  Note over Relay: per-peer durable inbox<br/>Bob can be offline
  Bob->>Relay: check_handoffs / inbox
  Relay-->>Bob: queued handoff
  Bob->>Relay: claim / accept
  Note over Bob,Agent: card / conv context<br/>board + pack attach
  Agent->>Relay: handoff @alice "done + notes"
  Relay-->>Alice: result lands in inbox
